snippet.title: EbiTapes - Official gameplay teaser
snippet.description:
EbiTapes is a wholesome musical adventure game.
Make your own delicious beats from the sounds you collect around the world. 
You'll have to make your own little mixtapes, and you'll give fun little concerts to the lovely people you meet on your way!
